column5: New tackle shop on HWY 7 east of Peterborough, was driving buy and spotted the sign, had to stop in. He's got lots a good stuff and fare prices:  BASS DEPOT WAREHOUSE, SW corner of HWY 7 & 28  Like I said not spam just a FYI.
Where the coffee shop it at the lights... or kitty corner to it?
Yes, he's between the boat dealer and the kayak/paddle boat place.
I was in the Gateway yesterday, twice and forgot all about the new tackle shop. Will be back early next week to pick up some parts and will check it out then.
this location would not show up in gps hotspot  so this would be useful for anyone heading out there,  u know stuff happens,  things get left behind like tackle, lures, license...
Thanks for the tip, Bill, will drop by on the way to the cottage to check it out...  Mike
